.PP
\fIMPUBytes=\fR
.RS 4
Rounds each packet (including overhead) up to the specified bytes\&. Takes an integer in the range 1\&...256\&. Defaults to unset and kernel\*(Aqs default is used\&.
.RE
.PP
\fICompensationMode=\fR
.RS 4
